WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:07.000
inspir exists for the moment a learner wants to understand something and needs a patient place to begin.

00:07.000 --> 00:15.000
The film introduces inspir as a free public learning companion for curiosity, practice, and access.

00:15.000 --> 00:23.000
The product is built around understanding, hints, quizzes, flashcards, and active learning loops.

00:23.000 --> 00:31.000
The closing promise is simple: learning should open instantly for anyone, anywhere.
